video.title: Free Rein
video.synopsis: A 15-year-old from LA spends the summer at her mom's childhood home on an island off the coast of England, where she bonds with a mysterious horse.

episodes.synopsis: When her sister Rosie goes missing after arriving at their grandfather's home, Zoe scours the area, meets some locals and has a scary encounter.
episodes.title: Raven

episodes.synopsis: When Mia insists on mounting Raven for a photo shoot, Zoe must calm the wild horse so he can be saddled. Rosie snoops in her mom's childhood diary.
episodes.title: Close Up

episodes.synopsis: To investigate her suspicions, Zoe defies her mom and sneaks off to the stables, where she has her first riding lesson and catches Pin red-handed.
episodes.title: Spying on Pin

episodes.synopsis: When Pin refuses to tell Zoe why he was stealing from the medical cabinet, she follows him home and finds out. Mia learns Zoe is not allowed to ride.
episodes.title: Pony Camp!

episodes.synopsis: Mia invites Rosie to a sleepover. Zoe and her friends find an engraved riding crop that may have been left behind by the horse thief.
episodes.title: The Sleepover

episodes.synopsis: Zoe learns why her mom forbade her from riding. Jade uncovers a secret about Raven's past. Becky proves to Ben that horses are better than quad bikes.
episodes.title: Horse Thief Hero

episodes.synopsis: Zoe learns more about Raven's mysterious origins. After finding what may be the real horse behind the ghost pony legend, Rosie realizes who "E" is.
episodes.title: Emerald

episodes.synopsis: Mia sabotages Zoe's plans for the barn dance. Becky sets a trap for the ghost pony, but she and her friends catch a suspected horse thief instead!
episodes.title: Pony Prom

episodes.synopsis: Ben helps Rosie trick her dad into calling her mom. While leading the kids on an islandwide search on horseback for Raven, Zoe has it out with Mia.
episodes.title: The Search

episodes.synopsis: The kids compete at the county show. An odd comment leads Zoe to realize who helped the horse thief, and sends her racing off to rescue Raven in time.
episodes.title: Show-down

episodes.synopsis: When rival riding school Holloway steals Bright Fields' recently won County Cup, Zoe and Pin must steal it back before Mia's press interview begins.
episodes.title: Rivals

episodes.synopsis: The gang sees Pin in a new light. On his last day, Marcus confesses a guilty secret to Rosie. Becky says a heartfelt goodbye to her longtime crush.
episodes.title: Golden Boy

episodes.synopsis: Things get out of hand during a jousting match at the annual Maid of the Island tournament when Zoe and Mia face off against Gaby from Holloway.
episodes.title: Maid of the Island

episodes.synopsis: At a beach party, a game of truth or dare forces Zoe to face her feelings for Pin, and a horse race on the sand leads her to betray Raven's trust.
episodes.title: Truth or Dare

episodes.synopsis: At Zoe's 16th birthday bash, Gaby stirs up trouble between Pin and Marcus, Rosie plays matchmaker, and Mia gathers proof of Callum's bad behavior.
episodes.title: Sweet 16

episodes.synopsis: Zoe takes Raven to a private spot to win his forgiveness. Becky, Ben and Rosie stumble upon a mysterious discovery. Mia overhears an upsetting chat.
episodes.title: Runaway

episodes.synopsis: A fire brings an unlikely hero to the rescue. Gaby reveals her painful past to Zoe and Pin. Jade comes through for Becky during a time of need.
episodes.title: Bob

episodes.synopsis: Gaby secretly trains on Raven, but Zoe's kindness makes her feel guilty. Rosie and Ben hunt for treasure in the tunnels. Pin makes plans with his mom.
episodes.title: Gaby

episodes.synopsis: After Zoe and Pin miss the ferry to Nationals, they get a ride in Grandpa Frank's van. But an empty gas tank leads to an unplanned stop at a fair.
episodes.title: Road Trip

episodes.synopsis: At Nationals, Pin does things his way, Becky cures Jade's fear of performing, Rosie uncovers an old family secret, and James tries to sabotage Raven.
episodes.title: Nationals

episodes.synopsis: The arrival of Zoe's mischievous cousin complicates the Bright Fields gang's attempts to impress the new mayor.
episodes.title: Wild Horses

episodes.synopsis: Pin leads the charge to find a skittish wild horse before the mayor does. The first Breakfast Club meeting leaves some riders champing at the bit.
episodes.title: Hunted

episodes.synopsis: Zoe and Gaby try to figure out what's wrong with Ariel. Marcus faces obstacles ahead of his trainer exam, and Mia undermines Susie.
episodes.title: Ariel

episodes.synopsis: The gang gallops into action after inviting the mayor to tea at the castle. As they train for tryouts, Zoe and Gaby grow increasingly competitive.
episodes.title: The Tea Party

episodes.synopsis: Bright Fields prepares to welcome a new four-legged guest, but Gaby's rivalry with Zoe could put the highly anticipated arrival at risk.
episodes.title: Foal O'Clock

episodes.synopsis: When Winnie's snobby schoolmates show up at Pony Camp, Zoe does everything possible to keep them busy. Meanwhile, Marcus pushes Mia to face her fears.
episodes.title: Pony Safari

episodes.synopsis: Gaby's need to win at tryouts jeopardizes her friendship with Zoe. Jade seeks answers when she loses track of the wild horses.
episodes.title: Tryouts

episodes.synopsis: As Zoe and her friends narrow down the list of suspects in their search for the wild horses, Pin becomes more and more unwell.
episodes.title: Princess

episodes.synopsis: Jade and Becky go sleuthing at the castle, Zoe makes a decision about her future, and Callum's obnoxious behavior gets on Gaby's nerves.
episodes.title: Victory Parade

episodes.synopsis: Zoe reaches out to her friends for help, Aaron lives out his cowboy dreams, and the gang finally solves the mystery of the wild horses' disappearance.
episodes.title: S.O.S.
